Importance of SEO, SEM, SMM: Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is a technical process to get a website in top 10 search results for any particular keyword. Why is SEO important and very helpful for marketing and increase in sales? The reason is simple, but the process of getting a website ranked in top 10 positions is complex. Most of the people who use search engines like Google, Bing or Yahoo; clicks on the websites which are displayed on the first page of Search Engine Results Page (SERP). Rarely people visit page two of search results. Imagine about the large number of global consumers (potential customers) that visits these search engines several times a day. SEO helps in simplification of complex marketing process because a large number of leads could reach your company via these search engines. Same is the case with Search Engine Marketing (SEM) and Social Media Management (SMM). In comparison to SEO, SEM is little bit different. SEM also contributes in increased traffic. SEO is an unpaid method of website promotion, whereas SEM is a paid method of website promotion. That's the difference between both. SEM is usually achieved through paid advertisements. SEM is little bit costlier than SEO, but the conversion rate is more compared to SEO. When both SEO and SEM are effective, and applied in a balanced manner; your company's sales rate will increase at a rapid speed. If we add SMM along side the SEO and SEM services, it would be the best option. A large number of traffic across the world visits social networking websites like facebook, twitter, linkedin, google plus, etc. If we put efforts on SMM along with SEO and SMM, then traffic from all angles will get diverted to your website. However, this is an ongoing process and takes time depending on what position your website currently is. More traffic on your website, means more sales, more publicity, more advertisement of company's products and/or services, and so on. The objective of every business is 'conversion of consumer to customer'. This challenge is achieved by searching the target consumer; who is looking for your product or service on internet; through my unique and exclusive methods of SEO, SEM and SMM. 

There are multiple areas where my skills, expertise and experience can help your company grow. I Hope for a fair opportunity to use my knowledge, skills, experience and expertise. 

Have a nice day,
